</P>
<P>
   The company expects earnings to miss analysts' expectations by
about 4 cents per share in the third quarter and by 4 cents to 6
cents in the fourth quarter. Sybron, a maker of laboratory
products, cited higher interest rates and the strong U.S. dollar.
</P>
