<HEADLINE> Boston Outfielder Disabled  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   BOSTON (AP) -- Boston's decimated outfield took another blow
Tuesday when right fielder Trot Nixon went on the disabled list
with an injured right hamstring.
</P>
<P>
   Nixon, one of the Red Sox' few steady hitters with a .293
