since June 19, and Darren Lewis is sidelined with tightness in his
left hamstring. Center fielder Carl Everett, who had a root-canal
procedure Tuesday, was replaced in the starting lineup by Curtis
Pride.
</P>
<P>
   The Red Sox called up Morgan Burkhart, who had 17 homers at
Pawtucket, to take Nixon's roster spot. Burkhart was designated
hitter Tuesday and singled in his first major-league at bat in the
second inning.
